==Oldest British people by region== [[Image:Henry Allingham in 2007.jpg|150px|thumb|right|[[Henry Allingham]] at the [[Imperial War Museum]] on 26 June 2006. Just before his death three years later at the age of 113, he would briefly become the oldest documented man in the world.]] This is a list of the oldest people by birth from each home nation, Crown dependency and [[British overseas territories|overseas territory]] of the United Kingdom - according to current borders.
