ast]], Northern Ireland |- |31 October 1973 |9 March 1974<br>({{age in days|1973|10|31|1974|3|9}} days) |[[Frederick Butterfield]] |align=center|M |109 &ndash; 110 |28 February 1864 &ndash; 9 March 1974<br> 110 years, 9 days |[[Harrogate]], England |- |9 March 1974 |24 December 1975<br> ({{age in years and days|1974|3|9|1975|12|24}}) |Rose Heeley |align=center|F |109 &ndash; 111 |25 August 1864 &ndash; 24 December 1975<br> 111 years, 121 days |[[Droitwich]], England |- |24 December 1975 |12 March 1976<br> ({{age in days|1975|12|24|1976|3|12}} days) |Agnes Helyar |align=center|F |109 |19 September 1866 &ndash; 12 March 1976<br> 109 years, 175 days |[[Abbots Langley]], England |- |12 March 1976 |12 February 1978<br> ({{age in years and days|1976|3|12|1978|2|12}}) |Sarah Morgan |align=center|F |109 &ndash; 111 |23 January 1867 &ndash; 12 February 1978<br> 111 years, 20 days |[[Tonbridge]], England |- |12 February 1978 |12 February 1979<br> ({{age in years and days|1978|2|12|1979|2|12}}) |Lilias Williams |align=center|F |109 &ndash; 110 |30 November 1868 &ndash; 12 February 1979<br> 110 years, 74 days |[[Launceston, Cornwall|Launceston]], England |- |12 February 1979 |20 October 1980<br> ({{age in years and days|1979|2|12|1980|10|20}}) |Florence Pannell |align=center|F |110 &ndash; 111 |26 December 1868 &ndash; 20 October 1980<br> 111 years, 299 days |[[Kensington]], England |- |20 October 1980 |5 January 1982<br> ({{age in years and days|1980|10|20|1982|1|5}}) |[[#Janetta Thomas|Janetta Thomas]] |align=center|F |110 &ndash; 112 |2 December 1869 &ndash; 5 January 1982<br> 112 years, 34 days |[[Cowbridge]], Wales |- |5 January 1982 |9 October 1982<br> ({{age in days|1982|1|5|1982|10|9}} days) |Alice Brewster |align=center|F |110 &ndash; 111 |16 September 1871 &ndash; 9 October 1982<br> 111 years, 23 days |[[Bath, Somerset|Bath]], England |- |9 October 1982 |27 December 1987<br> ({{age in years and days|1982|10|9|1987|12|27}}) |[[Anna Eliza Williams]] |align=center|F |109